{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.520", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.840", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.080", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlag ist zur Finanzierung der deutschen Einheit eingef\u00fchrt worden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.400", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Jahr\u00a02019 l\u00e4uft der Solidarpakt aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.800", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.920", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.000", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "entf\u00e4llt auch der Grund f\u00fcr diese Sonderabgabe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.200", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Konsequenterweise ist der Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlag abzuschaffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.200", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um das in aller Klarheit am Anfang zu sagen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.520", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Helmut Kohl, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.880", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der damalige Bundeskanzler, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.600", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat in den 1990er-Jahren gesagt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.680", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eDer Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlag ist bis Ende\u00a01999 endg\u00fcltig weg.\u201c Dann kam eine rot-gr\u00fcne Bundesregierung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.640", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann mit Fug und Recht sagen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.640", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch vor dem Hintergrund der damaligen Finanzsituation des Bundes\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.000", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Finanzierung der deutschen Einheit hat l\u00e4nger gedauert; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.840", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "machen wir uns an dieser Stelle nichts vor. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.160", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.760", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Helmut Kohl hat mit seinen Worten keinen Wahlkampf machen wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.280", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ging ihm nicht um politische Propaganda, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.040", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.360", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein politisches Versprechen einzul\u00f6sen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.800", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein Versprechen der deutschen Politik. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.800", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir als Freie Demokraten fordern heute vom Deutschen Bundestag ein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.920", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "genau dieses Versprechen einzuhalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.320", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.440", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will direkt in Richtung der Kolleginnen und Kollegen der Union sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.120", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verstecken Sie sich in dieser Frage nicht hinter den Sozialdemokraten!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.560", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hat doch nicht die SPD in den Verhandlungen zur Bildung der Gro\u00dfen Koalition durchgesetzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.800", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.000", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was jetzt im Koalitionsvertrag steht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist genau das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.160", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was die Union auch im Rahmen der Jamaika-Sondierungen f\u00fcr unverhandelbar erkl\u00e4rt hat."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.680", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist genau das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.040", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Sie wollten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.160", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Sie wollen genau das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.640", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.120", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Argumentation ist ja spannend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.120", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.800", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "insbesondere das Argument,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.440", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir h\u00e4tten uns bei Jamaika nicht ausreichend durchgesetzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.240", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie geben damit doch offiziell preis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.120", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Entlastung der Mitte der Gesellschaft nicht mehr das Anliegen der CDU/CSU ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.560", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.840", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es die Freien Demokraten im Deutschen Bundestag gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.240", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kollegen der Union."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.840", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will Ihnen noch einmal sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.280", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was das bedeutet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.160", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Argumentation heute lautet ja: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.400", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir machen zwei Jahre nach Auslaufen des Solidarpakts einen ersten Schritt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.600", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "90\u00a0Prozent der Zahler des Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlags brauchen ihn dann nicht mehr abzuf\u00fchren.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.400", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was bedeutet die Regelung zum Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.640", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie haben wollen und die im Koalitionsvertrag aufgegriffen worden ist? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.320", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie bedeutet doch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.000", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie den kleinen und mittelst\u00e4ndischen Unternehmen in Deutschland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.000", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Familienunternehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.480", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denjenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.760", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die w\u00e4hrend der Krisenjahre f\u00fcr die Mehrzahl der Arbeitspl\u00e4tze in Deutschland gesorgt haben und die Sie in Sonntagsreden immer wieder daf\u00fcr loben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.720", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denjenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.000", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich aufmachen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.280", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Digitalisierung zu bew\u00e4ltigen und daf\u00fcr Liquidit\u00e4t brauchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.120", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um neue Gesch\u00e4ftsmodelle auf den Weg zu bringen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.120", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den R\u00fccken zukehren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.800", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren der Union. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.320", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "An diesen Unternehmen begehen Sie in Wahrheit den Verrat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.920", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist der eigentliche Skandal in dieser Debatte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.760", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will zum Abschluss sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.400", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe die Debatten in der Union in den letzten Jahren beobachtet\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.560", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da ging es um die Abschaffung der Wehrpflicht und die Ehe f\u00fcr alle\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.080", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und festgestellt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.080", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man zweifelt und sich fragt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.400", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob man eigentlich noch konservativ genug ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.440", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich halte diese Debatte f\u00fcr Quatsch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.200", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.320", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist nicht das Problem. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.320", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Problem ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.040", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Union in Deutschland ihren ordnungspolitischen Kompass verloren hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.880", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben sich in Wahrheit vom Wohlstandsversprechen Ludwig Erhards verabschiedet."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.320", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht in dieser Frage um die Glaubw\u00fcrdigkeit deutscher Politik. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.120", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen sage ich auch aus strategischen Gr\u00fcnden: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.080", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Entscheidung \u00fcber den Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlag kann der Deutsche Bundestag alleine f\u00e4llen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.560", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er braucht daf\u00fcr nicht die L\u00e4nder. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.360", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verstecken Sie sich nicht hinter Ihrem Koalitionspartner! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.720", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verstecken Sie sich nicht hinter den Landesregierungen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.320", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nehmen Sie sich an der Mittelstandsunion in Ihren eigenen Reihen ein Beispiel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.520", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die gerade fordert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.560", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Soli f\u00fcr alle abgeschafft werden muss! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "295.200", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht um politische Hygiene und um die Glaubw\u00fcrdigkeit der deutschen Politik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "295.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "296.000", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um ein Versprechen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "296.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.640", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Sie in den 90er-Jahren gegeben haben. "
   ]
  }, 
